title: Skillfeed Game Development Fundamentals with Python
description:
Skillfeed Game Development Fundamentals with Python

In this course, instructor Alex Bowers will show you how to
successfully develop your very own computer game with the Python
programming language. He will walk you through the programming
of a game in which a monster will chase and try to eat your
character! You will learn how to create a game menu, how to
develop your characters and items, how to make your characters
move using key commands, and how to input different settings to
make your python game programming more challenging and fun!
